Your CloudPricing API Key
========================

Hi <%= @api_key.name %>,

Your API access request has been approved. Here's your key:

  <%= @token %>

SAVE THIS KEY NOW. It won't be shown again. If you lose it, you'll need to request a new one.

Quick Start
-----------

List LLM models:

  curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
    <%= @base_url %>/api/v1/llm_models

List cloud instances:

  curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
    <%= @base_url %>/api/v1/instances

Filter by provider:

  curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
    "<%= @base_url %>/api/v1/instances?providers[]=aws&vcpus_min=4"

Endpoints
---------

  GET /api/v1/instances        — Cloud instances (filterable)
  GET /api/v1/instances/:id    — Instance detail
  GET /api/v1/llm_models       — LLM models (filterable)
  GET /api/v1/llm_models/:id   — Model detail
  GET /api/v1/providers        — Cloud providers
  GET /api/v1/llm_providers    — LLM providers

Rate Limits
-----------

100 requests per minute. Check X-RateLimit-Remaining in response headers.

Happy building!
